- 'crown jewel of posts' refers to the most valuable or attractive post; 
- 'a thousand eyes' is a metaphor for more than 1000 total views; 
- 'intense discussions' implies at least 50 comments; 
- 'most glittering comments' means the highest average comment score.

- 'most viewed and most reacted posts' refers to posts ranked in the top 5 by either total views or total reactions; 
- 'past year' refers to the time period between '2023-01-01 00:00:00' and '2024-01-01 00:00:00'; 
- 'our community' refers to the community with community ID 0.
